{"id": "1466297858914259067", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 19, "author_id": "595478768659988490", "author_name": "aweonyu", "author_bot": false, "content": "안타깝네요", "timestamp": "2026-01-29T05:04:12.062000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["731807079140163674"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1466297802685546556", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1466297962232807555", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "256852230685196288", "author_name": "shrike784", "author_bot": false, "content": "엘바는 실드가 딜을 좀 얹어준단 느낌의 타격 캐릭터라", "timestamp": "2026-01-29T05:04:36.695000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1466298109998010613", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "256852230685196288", "author_name": "shrike784", "author_bot": false, "content": "슬더스 라이크라는 느낌으로 얘기하지만 사실 그 정도의 뻥튀기 시너지는 좀 빡셈", "timestamp": "2026-01-29T05:05:11.925000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1466298609770430701", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "595478768659988490", "author_name": "aweonyu", "author_bot": false, "content": "돌파템으로 타비랑 미리암 3초 2초씩 해둘까요?", "timestamp": "2026-01-29T05:07:11.080000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1466298817979748432", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "256852230685196288", "author_name": "shrike784", "author_bot": false, "content": "장기적으론 나쁘진 않은데 돌파템이 귀하니 일단 원하는 덱 타입에 맞춰서 그쪽에 투자할 애들을 정하는 게 좋을 듯", "timestamp": "2026-01-29T05:08:00.721000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1466298984388755640", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "595478768659988490", "author_name": "aweonyu", "author_bot": false, "content": "원하는 덱타입이 좀 단단한 덱 이긴합니다\n저 방밀전사가 매우 재밌을거 같았는데 아쉽네요", "timestamp": "2026-01-29T05:08:40.396000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1466299079259590801", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "256852230685196288", "author_name": "shrike784", "author_bot": false, "content": "그 방밀이라는 게 돌겜은 원래부터 방어도가 유지되고", "timestamp": "2026-01-29T05:09:03.015000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1466299116245225605", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "256852230685196288", "author_name": "shrike784", "author_bot": false, "content": "슬더스는 바리케이드 치면 전량 보존인데", "timestamp": "2026-01-29T05:09:11.833000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1466299141113249915", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "256852230685196288", "author_name": "shrike784", "author_bot": false, "content": "여기선 그럴 수단이 별로 없긴 해요", "timestamp": "2026-01-29T05:09:17.762000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1466299244531945535", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "256852230685196288", "author_name": "shrike784", "author_bot": false, "content": "그리고 방어도가 몇몇 수단 빼곤 최대체력 이상으로 올라가지 않음", "timestamp": "2026-01-29T05:09:42.419000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1466299391030857874", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "256852230685196288", "author_name": "shrike784", "author_bot": false, "content": "그래서 약간 딜레마가 생김", "timestamp": "2026-01-29T05:10:17.347000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1466299417798901884", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "256852230685196288", "author_name": "shrike784", "author_bot": false, "content": "방어도를 높게 쌓아서 때려죽일 정도면", "timestamp": "2026-01-29T05:10:23.729000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1466299433737130075", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "256852230685196288", "author_name": "shrike784", "author_bot": false, "content": "방어도가 무의미해진다는..", "timestamp": "2026-01-29T05:10:27.529000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1466299485926981674", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "595478768659988490", "author_name": "aweonyu", "author_bot": false, "content": "그럼 그냥체급되면서 때리는 덱이 재밌을듯요", "timestamp": "2026-01-29T05:10:39.972000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1466299524103540960", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "256852230685196288", "author_name": "shrike784", "author_bot": false, "content": "일단 타비는 미라클덱 타입이라 보시면 됨", "timestamp": "2026-01-29T05:10:49.074000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1466299554688401459", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "595478768659988490", "author_name": "aweonyu", "author_bot": false, "content": "골리아 쟤 첨에 걸렸는데 재밌더라구요", "timestamp": "2026-01-29T05:10:56.366000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1466299639324999904", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "595478768659988490", "author_name": "aweonyu", "author_bot": false, "content": "힘뺏는건 모르겠고 궁써서 쾅쾅쾅하는 맛이랄까", "timestamp": "2026-01-29T05:11:16.545000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1466299777405681725", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "595478768659988490", "author_name": "aweonyu", "author_bot": false, "content": "그래서 6돌까지 했는데 저거 힘강탈빼고 쓰레기레서 현타와서 접었던 기억이 있네요", "timestamp": "2026-01-29T05:11:49.466000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1466300229128163473", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "256852230685196288", "author_name": "shrike784", "author_bot": false, "content": "아무래도 파워인플레가 있다보니 지금 시점에선 후반부 컨텐츠까지 끌고 갈 딜러냐 라고 하면 애매하긴 하죠", "timestamp": "2026-01-29T05:13:37.165000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1466300581642764353", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "256852230685196288", "author_name": "shrike784", "author_bot": false, "content": "그래도 적 힘버프 몇이 되든 뺏어다 때린다는 게 메리트가 큼", "timestamp": "2026-01-29T05:15:01.211000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1466301246309925020", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "256852230685196288", "author_name": "shrike784", "author_bot": false, "content": "단단한 덱이라면 일단 카이커스를 중핵으로 놓고 반격덱을 짜는 게 괜찮을 듯", "timestamp": "2026-01-29T05:17:39.680000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
